  "title": "⛔️Petrol Station Attendant ⛔️URGENT (FUll & PART TIME) ‼️",
  "description": "<h3><strong>🟠Salary &amp; Benefits🟠</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>$1,700 – $1,800 per month</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Able to work rotate shift</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Full &amp; Part Time available</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Uniform and on-the-job training provided</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<h3><strong>➡️Responsibilities</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>Assist customers with fueling and ensure all <strong>safety procedures</strong> are followed</li>\n  <li>Provide friendly customer service and attend to basic inquiries</li>\n  <li>Maintain cleanliness of the <strong>forecourt and fueling area</strong></li>\n  <li>Report equipment faults or incidents promptly</li>\n</ul>\n<h3><strong>➡️Requirements</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>No prior experience required (training provided)</li>\n  <li>Physically fit, reliable, and safety-conscious</li>\n  <li>Able to work <strong>6 days a week</strong>, including <strong>weekends and rotating shifts</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>EA License No: 19C9611</p>\n<p>EA Personnel Reg No: R1433735 Teng Wei Mun (Celest)</p>",
